window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Enter Jeaniene Frost's Night Huntress series with this short story previously published in the <i>Death's Excellent Vacation</i> anthology. </p> <p>Vampires Cat Crawford and her husband Bones's romantic vacation is interrupted when they're enlisted to guard a spoiled heiress with both human and undead hitmen on her tail. Things quickly go from bad to worse when details of their assignment make their way through the supernatural grapevine, and what started as a simple bodyguard job ends up being a fight for survival that neither Cat nor Bones saw coming. </p>"; 
